  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Labor Program-Rule of Law in Ukraine, Mexico and South Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Ukraine, the Solidarity Center&apos;s Rule of Law staff is using their analysis of Ukraine&apos;s draft labor law to advocate for a legal reform process that complies with international legal norms and best practices. 

In Mexico, the Solidarity Center&apos;s Rule of Law staff is conducting an assessment on the extent to which Mexican law and practice complies with fundamental human and labor rights as established in the International Covenant on Economic, Social and Cultural Rights related with Articles 6, 7 and 8. 

In South Africa, the Solidarity Center&apos;s Rule of Law staff is working with its partners to broaden the enforcement of gender rights and maternity rights.</narrative>
  </description>
